@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_qvqhpo(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (v1 / (tmp * wp.abs(tmp + 0.41)))
    v1 = wp.sin(wp.cos((v2 + 0.64 * v1 + 0.03)))
    v2 = tmp
    tmp = v1
    tmp = (wp.sin(0.49) - wp.sin(v1))
    data[tid] = v0
